I mean this by how the course is "showing" us much less & "telling" us TOO MUCH, if that makes any sense? The paragraphs that the instructor is reading from are very good & explanatory, and I am learning from them, but perhaps bring a BIT MORE of these UP to the VIDEO side in bullet points, OR parse the paragraphs into M&P format so they are in bullet form where & when possible?  LETTERS, BULLETS and/or NUMBERING make learning quicker & easier. Just a suggestion.
